social_posts.post_text: 5 months old and she already knows how much fun dog rescue missions are 🥰 @allthingspupsrescue
Been so busy over the holidays that we had to have a joint belated bday party for 4 of the boys!! Grizzly is 7, Oso is 5, Sully is 5 and Elmo is 2 🎉 happiest birthday my loves 🐶❤️

From the streets of South East LA to winding up on the euth list at SEAACA to living the good life. Bean has done a complete transformation and wow is he the most perfect boy ever!! He is an absolute dream dog. Only one thing could make his life better. A forever home 🤎 Apply for Beanie Baby on our website allthingspupsrescue.org

Topher (who we’ve started calling Tofu) is still searching for his forever home! Toph is a young, silly, happy boy with the athleticism of a husky or shepherd. He is FAST and loves to run and play.

He has been without a loving family for the first part of his life which I’m sure was hard on him since he craves love and attention. He’s a lover and will want to be attached at your hip! He has separation anxiety and would do best with a family willing to be patient and work with him on this. He is crate trained and he’s definitely making progress with his separation anxiety already. 

He also LOVES his doggie friends, but is still learning about boundaries and social cues and often times doesn’t pick up on other dogs signals. He can definitely be in a home with other dogs. There is no aggression at all. He’s just a big dopey boy who wants to play! But sometimes he pushes other dogs buttons. This is a work in progress for Topher. 

Topher is house broken, crate trained, up to date on vaccines, neutered, microchipped, and heart worm negative.

If you’d like to meet him, please reach out or fill out an app on our website!
Tofu is looking for his people!! Hikers, runners, anyone who likes the outdoors, Tofu is your guy! He would be perfect for an active person/family. He has so much love to give 🐾
Sweet Tucker working through his anxiety and reactivity towards new people and dogs with our Phoenix trainer Kailani ❤️
Do you like sunshine, swimming, and the outdoors? If so, meet your new adventure buddy, Tofu! Apply to adopt him on our website 🖤
Alright San Diego, start lining up to meet Mack! All 160 lbs of him is ready for adoption 🐾

Okay everyone, let’s get this video shared as many times as we can to help Fisher find a foster or adopter! And if you’ve been following Fisher’s training progress, peep the clips here that show how amazing he is with walking now 💙🐾

Another (human) baby joining the pack soon ❤️

Photo by @natalie.vell 
Glam by @dorinarotari_muah
SAY HELLO TO OUR NEW BABY ❤️

My first baby is TEN 🥹🥹🥹
Juneau Rose- my soul dog and my literal everything. She saved my life. I adopted Juneau when I was in a very dark and depressed place. She gave me the courage to get out of the toxic lifestyle I was living and had been raised in and move across the country to pursue my dreams. Anyone who knows Juneau knows she isn’t just a dog, she’s a literal human and it’s kind of creepy at times lol. She’s been glued to my side from day 1 and always just knows what I’m thinking or need. We are connected in a way I could never put into words. Her intelligence, fierce loyalty, passion and snuggly nature is unmatched. I will never meet a dog like her ever again, she is truly one of a kind. Happy 10th birthday Juneau I love you beyond words 🤍🤍🤍
Morning routine with Malibu and the bears when the dog nanny and baby nanny are out of town 🐶💕

HAPPY BIRTHDAY TO MY SWEET BOYS 🐾❤️ Celebrating Nemo’s 1st birthday and Zion’s 4th birthday 🎉 I could not be more grateful for both of these fur babies. Nemo has just been the biggest bundle of joy and best addition to our family. Zion is the silliest as always and just the best big brother to Nemo and Malibu ❤️❤️❤️ I love them so much

One month of Posie 🌸 

I’ve been kind of MIA the past couple years having human babies but am excited to say I’m back!! For those who have followed my journey on my personal Instagram, I will only be posting on @allthingspups now 🐶❤️ excited to share my unfiltered crazy life with 101 dogs and babies with you all, while of course still sharing training knowledge and showing all things dog!
